## Modifications from upstream

xiaoyao-pdf fork applies the following modifications relative to upstream
Stirling-PDF v2.14.0. All modifications are licensed under Apache 2.0 by
the xiaoyao-pdf contributors.

1. **Brand replacement** — "Stirling-PDF" / "Stirling" replaced with
   "xiaoyao-pdf" / "xiaoyao" in user-facing text (UI labels, settings.yml
   defaults, email templates, static HTML pages). NOT replaced in:
   - Package names (`stirling.software.*`)
   - Class names (`StirlingPDF`, `SPDFApplication`)
   - LICENSE / NOTICE attribution text
   - GitHub URLs pointing to Stirling-Tools/Stirling-PDF repo
2. **Internal/air-gapped defaults** — PostHog / Scarf / OIDC / SAML2 /
   AATL / EUTL / remote version check / remote TSA all default to off
   or to internal placeholders (see `docs/internal-deployment.md`).
3. **Default security** — `security.enableLogin: true`, initial admin
   user pre-seeded to "admin", login agreement popup enabled by default
   with `customFiles/disclaimer/zh-CN.md`.
4. **Design tokens** — `frontend/editor/src/core/theme/` defines
   xiaoyao-pdf brand color (#0F3D3E), spacing, typography. Does not
   replace any existing component library.
5. **License file** — Apache License 2.0 with explicit attribution to
   Stirling-Tools/Stirling-PDF.

